Role Description
================

Install and configure {{ role_name }} on a system.

Example Playbook
================

This example is taken from `molecule/default/playbook.yml` and is tested on each push, pull request and release.

```yaml
---
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Install and configure {{ role_name }}
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
- name: {{ role_name }}
  hosts: all
  become: true
  gather_facts: false

  roles:
    - role: tehtbl.bootstrap
    - role: tehtbl.{{ role_name }}
      {{ role_name }}_parameter: value
```

